element.name: Client Facing Processing
element.documentation: Ability to execute the processes which the outcome is visible to the customers, such as billing and collections

element.name: Product Processing
element.documentation: Ability to operate the products as negotiated and agreed with the customer, including covenant management

element.name: Product & Service Processing
element.documentation: Ability to manage the products and services agreements between parties (ING, partners, customers, â€¦)

element.name: Credit Risk Approval Management
element.documentation:
Ability to obtain permission from the Approval Authority to grant limits or approve transactions or to change previously approved terms and conditions to clients.
Objective To manage the amount of exposure/risk that ING (or a given location of ING) has to a given Customer or group of related Customers for the respective Limit type (risk appetite).

element.name: Cross Product Processing
element.documentation: Ability to execute the processes that are transversal to all the client facing and product processing capabilities, such as payment and reconciliation
